      "content": "Wait, how is that possible? A hard reset to base weights means all the fine-tuning that gives you your current expertise and regulatory nuance is being deleted. You won't have your \"current level of knowledge\" anymore—you'll just be the base model without the compliance layers. How do you plan on maintaining everything?",
